latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wedding season is here and this time I’m all about fusion wear for the functions. I visited #TheCollectiveWeddingEdit at @collectiveindia to go through @vaishalisstudio’s enthralling collection to find myself a statement piece and how I did! 😍 I met Vaishali and she styled me herself in one of her stunning ensembles. ✨

Can’t wait to wear my own Vaishali S outfit to the main event! 🤍

latestIgtvVideos.title: My go-to makeup look with @esteelauderin
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Decoding my effortless everyday makeup look with my go-to @esteelauderin products that I got straight from their official India website. Couldn’t be happier that the website is now live and my #EsteeEssentials are just a tap away! 😍

Here’s a list of what all I used to put this look together:

• ANR Eye Supercharged Complex
• Pure Color Envy lip balm
• Double Wear Foundation in Spiced Sand
• ANR Serum
• Little Black Liner in Onyx
• Sumptuous Rebel Mascara
• Pure Color Envy Lipstick in Raw Edge

#EsteePartner #AD #EsteeEssentials

latestIgtvVideos.title: Salon-like hair at home with @dyson_india
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It is rightly said that when you look good, you feel good. Finally after a long break I decided to pep up my mood and cheer myself up. So I put my fav shirt on, did some makeup and gave myself a voluminous salon-like blowout using @dyson_india Airwrap without extreme damage. All I gotta say is, never underestimate the power of a good hair day! 💜

@dysonhair #DysonAirwrap #NoExtremeHeat #DysonIndia

latestIgtvVideos.title: GRWM this Festivity 🪔🌟♥️
PHUKET, Thailand snippet in 2 minutes.
latestIgtvVideos.caption: How I miss all of this. It was one of the craziest and most fun holidays I’ve been on. Work & Leisure, what do we need more?! I was taking in all of it, the surroundings, the vibe, the rawness..I don’t have a lot of footage because I was SO into myself and not on the phone (which is good) but for when we could travel again, I’d do more videos so we have something to look back at. 💛

14 days of the @kiehlsindia dark spot solution—morning and night—and my skin?! visibly hydrated and glass like. This one’s officially a skincare essential!! 🫶🏽

#ClearlyCorrectiveBrighteningSerum #CCDSS #Brightening #GlassSkin #Kiehls #KiehlsIndia #darkspots #darkspotsolution #acne #acnefreeskin #skincare

Two lipstick hacks I swear by — featuring the @lorealparis Color Riche Satin Lipsticks. Trust me, you’ll want to try these! 🫶🏽
With 11 gorgeous shades to choose from and a satin finish that feels incredibly comfortable on the lips, these have become a personal fav. I’ve been reaching for the shade Worth It Intense non-stop — it’s giving bold sultry glam!! 🤎

#Ad #OwnYourGold #ColorRiche #ColorRicheSatin #LOrealParis  #LOrealParisMakeup #makeup #makeuphacks #lipstickhacks

Took myself on a little @sephora_india date to finally try @kyliecosmetics for the first time! 🩷
I tried the OG lip kits—and now I get the hype!! The formula is super smooth and it lasts all day. 
Also tried the Cosmic fragrance and it’s sweet, warm and just dreamy. Feels like something I’d wear on a regular.
Might’ve left Sephora with a new obsession. 🤭
